snippet.title: Cloudberry Kingdom - the impossible gameplay trailer [DE]
snippet.description:
Meet Bob and his friends. Trying to find the way out in those mad levels. If we can do it on this gameplay trailer, can you do it as well ? Will you survive ? No, probably not. But hey, it's worth a shot
